<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Welcome to <%= schoolName %> Admin Portal</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
        color: #333;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      .container {
        width: 90%;
        margin: 0 auto;
        max-width: 600px;
        background-color: #fff;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }
      .header {
        text-align: center;
        background-color: #ff5722;
        color: white;
        padding: 10px 0;
        border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 30px;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 0.9em;
        color: #777;
      }
      .footer a {
        color: #ff5722;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
      .btn {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        background-color: #ff5722;
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
        margin-top: 20px;
      }
      .important {
        font-weight: bold;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>Welcome to <%= schoolName %>, <%= firstName %>!</h1>
      </div>

      <div class="content">
        <p>Dear <%= firstName %>,</p>

        <p>
          Welcome to <strong><%= schoolName %></strong>! We are thrilled to have
          you as part of our administration team. Below are your login
          credentials to access the admin portal:
        </p>

        <p><strong>username:</strong> <%= username %></p>
        <p><strong>Password:</strong> <%= password %></p>

        <p>
          Please log in and change your password as soon as possible for
          security purposes.
        </p>

        <a href="#" class="btn">Log in to the Admin Portal</a>

        <p>
          If you encounter any issues or need assistance, feel free to reach out
          to our support team. We are here to help you.
        </p>

        <p>
          Welcome once again, and we look forward to your leadership at <%=
          schoolName %>!
        </p>

        <p>Best regards,</p>
        <p><strong>The <%= schoolName %> Team</strong></p>
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        <p>
          For any questions, please reply to this email or visit our
          <a href="#">Support Page</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
